TopicTitle: A .90 play through with Adios tech tree.

Articles.Content:
Hey all!

I started uploading videos again to my YouTube. This is my Let's Play with the Adios Tech Tree, and a few other mods. I'd love some feedback, suggestions, whatever. I'm shooting for posting new uploads 3 times a week. There is litteraly no production value or frills. Just me trying to talk and play some awesome KSP ( not nearly as easy at it seems ) let me know what you think.

Thanks!!
